name: Airdrop Llama
description:
Thank you to everyone for collecting my first series of llamas. Your continued support means so much to me. Because of you, I got my start in this NFT world. I am forever grateful.

To my top 5 collectors, please enjoy this special “Airdrop Llama,” made just for you :)

“The meaning of life is to find your gift. The purpose of life is to give it away.” - Pablo Picasso
